    SQLiteIdentityIndex<A extends Comparable<A>,​O>
    An index which allows objects to be persisted directly in the index in serialized form, and to be accessed using a primary key attribute (as obtained from a foreign key held elsewhere).
    SQLiteIndex<A extends Comparable<A>,​O,​K>
    An index backed by a table in a SQLite database.
    SQLiteIndexFlags
    Flags which can be set in query options (via QueryFactory) which allow the behaviour of SQLiteIndex to be adjusted.
    SQLiteIndexFlags.BulkImportExternallyManged
